1
00:00:13,820 --> 00:00:15,740
♪Showing my weakness is a facade♪

2
00:00:15,740 --> 00:00:17,540
♪The aim is to lure you into the trap♪

3
00:00:17,540 --> 00:00:19,140
♪You can only see clearly♪

4
00:00:19,140 --> 00:00:21,300
♪If you sacrifice all your naivety♪

5
00:00:21,300 --> 00:00:23,380
♪This hunting game♪

6
00:00:23,380 --> 00:00:25,180
♪Trust is doubtful♪

7
00:00:25,180 --> 00:00:28,780
♪Seducing is also a kind of trick♪

8
00:00:28,780 --> 00:00:31,540
♪Who is still fantasizing♪

9
00:00:31,540 --> 00:00:32,860
♪Longing and hoping for a miracle?♪

10
00:00:32,860 --> 00:00:35,100
♪Who has eyes♪

11
00:00:35,100 --> 00:00:36,700
♪Filled with helplessness,
despair and devoid of light?♪

12
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:38,780
♪Who is still waiting♪

13
00:00:38,780 --> 00:00:40,340
♪For the broken soul to be warmed?♪

14
00:00:40,340 --> 00:00:45,780
♪Who finally chooses to move forward?♪

15
00:00:45,780 --> 00:00:49,620
♪I will crush and trample every danger♪

16
00:00:49,620 --> 00:00:53,740
♪Strategising step by step.
Taking initiative to begin the game♪

17
00:00:53,740 --> 00:00:57,500
♪Taking control of the game.
Love should not be compromised♪

18
00:00:57,500 --> 00:01:00,780
♪Disguise is just an opening song♪

19
00:01:00,780 --> 00:01:03,460
♪I will be patient and cautious♪

20
00:01:03,460 --> 00:01:05,180
♪Controlling the end in the shadows♪

21
00:01:05,180 --> 00:01:07,100
♪You are unexpected,♪

22
00:01:07,100 --> 00:01:09,660
♪The biggest surprise
given to me by God♪

23
00:01:09,660 --> 00:01:14,100
♪Let's welcome the dawn
after a dark night together♪

24
00:01:14,500 --> 00:01:17,580
♪Before embracing each other
and breaking out of this with love♪

25
00:01:18,240 --> 00:01:21,880
=Her Disguise=
(Adapted from Shuiyue Xianling's novel, "Her Disguise")

26
00:01:22,140 --> 00:01:24,860
=Episode 13=

27
00:01:38,879 --> 00:01:40,840
I can help you
remove this piece of glass.

28
00:01:41,760 --> 00:01:42,480
But...

29
00:01:42,547 --> 00:01:45,197
♪Watching the sunset alone♪

30
00:01:45,239 --> 00:01:46,040
There is no anesthetic.

31
00:01:46,087 --> 00:01:48,040
♪Falling asleep in solitude♪

32
00:01:49,027 --> 00:01:50,732
♪When I miss you♪

33
00:01:50,760 --> 00:01:51,840
Stop talking.

34
00:01:52,840 --> 00:01:54,319
If you ruin this arm,

35
00:01:55,760 --> 00:01:57,200
I'll never let you go.

36
00:01:57,316 --> 00:02:01,840
♪In the stillness, memories drift back♪

37
00:02:02,441 --> 00:02:09,241
♪Yesterday's whispers
linger softly in my ear♪

38
00:02:09,987 --> 00:02:16,036
♪The evening stars are dull without you♪

39
00:02:17,490 --> 00:02:22,848
♪Words can't express
how much I missed you when we reunited♪

40
00:02:24,824 --> 00:02:30,579
♪I avoid your burning gaze♪

41
00:02:30,707 --> 00:02:31,296
♪Words unspoken♪

42
00:02:31,319 --> 00:02:34,000
Why were those workers

43
00:02:34,439 --> 00:02:35,800
so resentful towards you earlier?

44
00:02:36,024 --> 00:02:39,590
♪The evening breeze whispers, I'm weary♪

45
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:42,319
I think someone is trying

46
00:02:43,039 --> 00:02:44,240
to frame me to get the map.

47
00:02:45,280 --> 00:02:46,360
What's so important

48
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:48,680
about that map?

49
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:50,400
Is it worth protecting like this?

50
00:02:51,464 --> 00:02:54,703
♪The evening breeze says, I'm tired♪

51
00:02:55,520 --> 00:02:57,919
Ten years ago,

52
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:01,439
the Lin faction lost to the Lian faction

53
00:03:01,879 --> 00:03:03,360
and hid an arsenal

54
00:03:04,120 --> 00:03:06,080
in a secret location.

55
00:03:06,639 --> 00:03:08,000
Back then, my father

56
00:03:08,330 --> 00:03:09,970
had a close relationship
with the Lin faction.

57
00:03:10,599 --> 00:03:12,599
On his deathbed, he warned me

58
00:03:13,639 --> 00:03:15,120
that Marshal Lian

59
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:18,879
was wicked and immoral.

60
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:21,479
At that time, I vowed

61
00:03:21,517 --> 00:03:23,459
♪The evening stars are dull without you♪

62
00:03:23,479 --> 00:03:24,360
to protect

63
00:03:26,159 --> 00:03:28,319
this at all costs.

64
00:03:28,346 --> 00:03:33,066
♪Words can't express
how much I missed you when we reunited♪

65
00:03:33,199 --> 00:03:33,680
You...

66
00:03:34,240 --> 00:03:36,280
Haven't you always hoped for my death?

67
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:37,319
Look,

68
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:40,199
your wish is coming true soon.

69
00:03:41,056 --> 00:03:43,200
♪Words unspoken,
feeling the depth alone♪

70
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:44,800
I just know that a doctor

71
00:03:45,439 --> 00:03:47,680
has to save lives.

72
00:03:47,716 --> 00:03:49,619
♪The evening breeze whispers, I'm weary♪

73
00:03:50,281 --> 00:03:54,826
♪Those who shared the breeze have left♪

74
00:03:54,890 --> 00:03:59,287
♪I linger at the crossroads of the past♪

75
00:03:59,304 --> 00:04:02,030
♪Tears falling freely♪

76
00:04:02,099 --> 00:04:05,333
♪The evening breeze says, I'm tired♪

77
00:04:06,280 --> 00:04:07,560
At least you've got a conscience.

78
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:11,719
Guess saving you twice was worth it.

79
00:04:12,511 --> 00:04:15,073
♪Yet I won't give up♪

80
00:04:15,083 --> 00:04:18,133
♪The evening breeze whispers, I'm weary♪

81
00:04:18,516 --> 00:04:22,979
♪Those who shared the breeze have left♪

82
00:04:23,066 --> 00:04:29,849
♪In time, I gently let go♪

83
00:04:30,050 --> 00:04:33,076
♪Of our memories♪

84
00:04:52,334 --> 00:04:55,835
♪A strange rain in the early morning♪

85
00:04:56,375 --> 00:04:59,815
♪Drops falling silently♪

86
00:04:59,910 --> 00:05:03,469
♪Coming and going♪

87
00:05:03,866 --> 00:05:07,607
♪Even the end is as swift as the tides♪

88
00:05:08,453 --> 00:05:11,842
♪I want to remember
the stranger you are♪

89
00:05:12,254 --> 00:05:15,966
♪Leaving some space
on the edge of the crowd♪

90
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:19,614
♪To hold onto the memories♪

91
00:05:19,907 --> 00:05:23,917
♪Can it delay its fading
by just a second?♪

92
00:05:24,935 --> 00:05:27,776
♪Too close and it suffocates♪

93
00:05:27,796 --> 00:05:31,983
♪Wanting to love
yet needing to detach anytime♪

94
00:05:32,450 --> 00:05:33,852
♪Deeply etched in my heart♪

95
00:05:33,939 --> 00:05:40,223
♪How can your traces
be erased so easily?♪

96
00:05:40,429 --> 00:05:46,412
♪You are the strange rain in my world♪

97
00:05:48,443 --> 00:05:54,009
♪Words drowned in the lonely night♪

98
00:05:56,363 --> 00:05:59,037
♪Your name pulls me under♪

99
00:05:59,040 --> 00:06:00,199
Do you not regret

100
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:02,839
being schemed against

101
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:04,600
and hunted down

102
00:06:07,959 --> 00:06:08,879
for this map?

103
00:06:11,879 --> 00:06:12,639
And what about you?

104
00:06:12,681 --> 00:06:14,800
♪Raindrops blown into my eyes
by the wind♪

105
00:06:14,839 --> 00:06:16,240
Do you not regret

106
00:06:16,240 --> 00:06:17,240
losing everything

107
00:06:18,759 --> 00:06:19,720
for your friends?

108
00:06:20,349 --> 00:06:25,966
♪I finally see clearly♪

109
00:06:28,460 --> 00:06:33,059
♪Only understanding the meaning
in the end♪

110
00:06:33,716 --> 00:06:38,053
♪The rain stopped and I lost it♪

111
00:06:49,519 --> 00:06:51,680
He ran away. We didn't get him.

112
00:07:01,120 --> 00:07:02,199
Go to hell.

113
00:07:07,573 --> 00:07:11,500
(Workers' wage dispute sparks outrage.
Lu's company in crisis.)

114
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:19,480
The world is truly tough.

115
00:07:21,140 --> 00:07:23,160
Was it the Qin family's car
that took you home last night?

116
00:07:28,199 --> 00:07:29,199
I asked you

117
00:07:30,439 --> 00:07:31,879
to pick up Mange, didn't I?

118
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:33,920
He,

119
00:07:34,360 --> 00:07:35,839
what kind of woman can't you get?

120
00:07:36,199 --> 00:07:37,759
That woman causes trouble.

121
00:07:38,010 --> 00:07:39,580
It's better to let her leave
the Lu family.

122
00:07:44,560 --> 00:07:46,360
Eldest Young Master,
breakfast is prepared.

123
00:07:46,519 --> 00:07:47,439
Please, have your meal.

124
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:52,399
Guanghe.

125
00:07:55,120 --> 00:07:55,639
Lu Haoran.

126
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:04,990
Where did you go last night?

127
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:05,759
You didn't come back.

128
00:08:08,040 --> 00:08:09,800
Yesterday, I had Mange
stay with me all night.

129
00:08:11,120 --> 00:08:11,800
Guanghe.

130
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:14,199
Let's talk about it tomorrow.

131
00:08:15,399 --> 00:08:17,399
I'm too tired and worn out.

132
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:18,800
Not now.

133
00:08:22,480 --> 00:08:23,040
Mange.

134
00:08:23,200 --> 00:08:24,460
What did you guys do last night?

135
00:08:25,680 --> 00:08:27,560
Guanghe, I'm tired too.

136
00:08:33,960 --> 00:08:34,519
Mange.

137
00:08:36,039 --> 00:08:36,720
I've decided.

138
00:08:38,300 --> 00:08:39,120
We're getting married

139
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:42,200
next month.

140
00:08:47,799 --> 00:08:48,320
Okay.

141
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:26,890
Eldest Young Master Lu,

142
00:09:27,279 --> 00:09:28,480
have you made a decision?

143
00:09:35,300 --> 00:09:36,130
Eldest Young Master Lu.

144
00:09:40,399 --> 00:09:42,080
Was Lin Mange with you just now?

145
00:09:42,639 --> 00:09:43,320
Don't worry.

146
00:09:43,799 --> 00:09:45,399
I won't touch Ms. Lin.

147
00:09:46,360 --> 00:09:47,759
Didn't we agree

148
00:09:48,639 --> 00:09:51,480
to play the long game?

149
00:09:52,320 --> 00:09:54,120
As long as this move is executed well,

150
00:09:54,919 --> 00:09:56,399
both the woman and the map

151
00:09:57,399 --> 00:09:59,360
will be ours.

152
00:10:01,879 --> 00:10:02,360
Master Qin.

153
00:10:03,700 --> 00:10:05,290
Actually, I can
find someone else for you.

154
00:10:06,240 --> 00:10:08,279
Lin Mange isn't really suitable.

155
00:10:08,519 --> 00:10:09,320
No, no, no.

156
00:10:09,679 --> 00:10:10,960
She's perfect.

157
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:14,279
Lu Haoran says the map is missing,

158
00:10:15,799 --> 00:10:17,320
but I believe

159
00:10:17,720 --> 00:10:19,559
it's with your fiancee.

160
00:10:21,960 --> 00:10:23,240
But your brother

161
00:10:23,480 --> 00:10:26,360
is quite attentive to your fiancee.

162
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:28,480
You don't know what he just did...

163
00:10:36,039 --> 00:10:36,519
Okay.

164
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:39,080
Let's do it your way.

165
00:10:48,450 --> 00:10:49,690
Have you all sorted things out?

166
00:10:59,140 --> 00:11:02,180
♪Bye, weakness♪

167
00:11:03,100 --> 00:11:11,100
♪Missed opportunities sink
into the ocean with the setting sun♪

168
00:11:12,140 --> 00:11:17,980
♪Butterfly leaves the land of taboo♪

169
00:11:18,860 --> 00:11:23,260
♪The rotten mud rots away the malice♪

170
00:11:26,980 --> 00:11:32,020
♪The fallen
naively wipes away the color♪

171
00:11:32,780 --> 00:11:39,220
♪The soul wakes up
in the dangerous forest♪

172
00:11:40,620 --> 00:11:46,420
♪Crushing the mundane
and ever changing mask step by step♪

173
00:11:46,420 --> 00:11:51,900
♪The crow stops whispering in the fog♪

174
00:11:52,860 --> 00:12:00,700
♪Black rose blooms
at the end of the abyss♪

175
00:12:00,700 --> 00:12:06,500
♪It is a beautiful scar on my wound♪

176
00:12:07,060 --> 00:12:09,980
♪Overcoming hardships♪

177
00:12:09,980 --> 00:12:16,300
♪A strong armor
wards off criticisms and disputes♪

178
00:12:16,940 --> 00:12:20,860
♪My brilliant life♪

179
00:12:21,420 --> 00:12:25,380
♪No matter who says anything♪

180
00:12:25,380 --> 00:12:29,060
♪I won't be hurt anymore♪

181
00:12:29,060 --> 00:12:35,380
♪If kindness goes away,
I'd rather be sharp♪
